{"tid":1524281,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"2/9 2030 開始每日落最近港鐵 個個站都圍佢投訴佢 assemble","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:02:07.000Z","uid":27203,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8174b013dcf42b2b18e62069723f283b1d6c9ce8","tid":1524281,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:56:53.000Z","msg":"屌你港鐵封站做幫兇 勇武冇退路都冇人講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501429</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n講撚左一定要清算黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要每個站都圍撚曬佢 和理非200萬人都落黎<br />\n去最近個站 街坊裝<br />\n我睇你班黨鐵狗仔點撚樣清 點撚樣落閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同你講 人少先最危險<br />\n望撚到恐襲都唔幫拖就咪撚做香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔需要勇武<br />\n我需要日日圍撚住佢到關站<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪撚同我講咩禁制令<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔係阻佢運作<br />\n係要投訴班撚屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日日圍 <br />\n係日日圍<br />\n香港人 手足為你犧牲得太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做番少少野得唔得<br />\n<br />\n日期：2/9 - 跪低<br />\n時間：20:30 - 關站<br />\n地點：最近黨鐵<br />\n衣物：街坊<br />\n人數：最少200萬<br />\n<br />\n和理非 assemble<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d556b074b502446c69a102324424716d0e510005","tid":1524281,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:57:01.000Z","msg":"推啦屌"},{"pid":"aac54ff6825dcfb617ced45e80050fc73e04f6a2","tid":1524281,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0